high_descs: walk to the sofa.
Take the knife that is on the sofa.
Walk around to the other side of the sofa and cut the apple that is on the sofa.
walk out of the room.
Go to the kitchen fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
turn around and make a left to get into the living room sofa.
Go to the sofa and pick up a piece of the apple that was sliced.
Turn around and make a left and walk to the other side of the room to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and heat it up, then take out the apple from the microwave.
Go to the fridge and stand in front of it.
Open the fridge and put the apple in it.
anns.task_desc: Getting an Apple and putting it in the Fridge.

high_descs: Move to the right of the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the couch.
Move to the left side of the couch.
Cut the apple on the couch with the knife.
Head to the fridge across the room.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and walk back to the left side of the sofa.
Pick up the apple from the couch.
Head to the microwave across the room.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave and take it out.
Turn right to face the fridge.
Put the apple slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated apple slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Step to the right side of the sofa in front of you.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Move to the left side of the sofa.
Cut an apple on the sofa with the knife.
Walk across the hall to its opposite corner where you find a kitchen corner, and approach a fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Go back to the left side of the sofa with the cut fruit.
Pick up an apple slice from the sofa.
Head back to the kitchen corner, but approach a microwave to the left of the fridge.
Put the apple slice in the microwave, heat it up for a while, then take it back out.
Step right in front of the fridge.
Put the apple slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated-up apple slice in the fridge
